            <lg xml:id="TK567">
<l>kaṭumoḻiyuṅ kaiyikanta taṇṭamum vēnta </l>
<l> ṉaṭumuraṇ ṭēykku maram</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Severe words and excessive punishments will be a file to waste away a king's power for destroying (his enemies).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
